data.description:
New flooring being installed in all 3 bedrooms!  
Welcome Home! Step into a modernized kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances, complemented by newer cabinets and a convenient double-oven. The tile floors add a touch of sophistication, and the new sliding glass door bathes the space in natural light. The front of the house showcases newer windows, enhancing both aesthetic appeal and energy efficiency.  Discover a remodeled master shower, new light fixtures, and a host of additional updates that make this property stand out. For added utility, the backyard shed comes equipped with power, offering endless possibilities for a workshop or storage.
Enjoy the extended driveway and front porch. The spacious backyard offers a brand new privacy fence and a back patio with a firepit.  Alternatively, cozy up indoors next to the wood-burning fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for those chilly evenings.
Don't miss out on the chance to call 1223 Cimmaron Dr. your home. Book an appointment today and seize the opportunity to make this meticulously updated residence your own.
